name: Hund
description: Introducing HUND, a meme coin launched on Solana that brings together the excitement of memes with practical utility tools like HundSwap and HundPad. Founded by crypto influencer MuroCrypto, HUND aims to capitalize on the popularity of meme coins while ensuring project longevity through its diverse ecosystem. With a total supply of 500 million tokens, HUND maintains a healthy circulation of 250 million tokens, with the remaining tokens strategically held by MuroCrypto for future burns, marketing initiatives, and development purposes. Join the HUND community today and experience the best of both worlds - memes and utility!
